tr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pda1665702735767.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pda1665702735767.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pda1665702735767.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pda1665702735767\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Microsoft SQL Server \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Microsoft SQL Server DBMS connector (MSS) enables you to integrate MS SQL\n      databases with Uniface.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pda1665702735767__section_w522ab1b5b1_w523ab1b5_w524ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Connector Feature</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Mnemonic:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MSS</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported Version:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">For the supported platforms and product versions, see the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://community.rocketsoftware.com/rocket-uniface-forum-home-20/uniface-product-availability-information-18191\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Platform Availability Matrix</a>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported utilities</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Create Table, Create Script, and Load Definitions, are all supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">SQL support</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Stored procedures support</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pda1665702735767__table_d4775e1_d4776e1_d4777e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uzu1665702542108.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>DBMS Connector Overview</a><p>This section provides an overview of supported functionality and limitations for all DBMS connectors.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"